name: 808s & HEARTBREAK
description: 808s & HEARTBREAK The CD by Kanye West that creatively inspired me and got me through the initial abduction period of my daughter Nadia Lynn. Ironically she was born in August of 2008 (8.08) and her abduction has left me heartbroken. This entire cd was the personification of my life experiences at the moment and how I felt as an individual at the time. It is a classic to me and this is my tribute capturing that moment in time. Check out the design process for this shirt HERE Sizing * I am wearing size small in the picture - I am 6'0ft 165lbs *

name: NY STATE OF MIND
description: Limited Edition New York Series The state of New York has truly been an inspiration to me as an individual. name: NO LOVE
description: EMPTEES This shirt is a tribute to the design forum that helped me grow as a designer. This design is a play off of the original emptees forum shirt designed by Geoff May. This shirt features a lock inside a golden heart representing the fact that my first design posts back in 2008 were so amateur that the forum thread was locked. Through the rejection, I managed to learn a lot from the designers and other successful brands on there. Any aspiring graphic designers or clothing line owners, I would suggest you check out the forum, there's incredible talent there, but if you decide to go make sure your design work is up to par before posting it for critiques. Trust me. Sizing * I am wearing size small in the picture - I am 6'0ft 165lbs *

name: FASHION ASYLUM
description: THE FASHION ASYLUM Shirt designed during the immediate period after my daughters abduction. I was literally losing my mind, and to keep some sort of sanity I designed shirts. This shirt in particular is symbolic of this time where I thought that the loss of my daughter would inadvertently cause me to sacrifice my dreams of running my clothing line. Not knowing how I would achieve success or even see my daughter again drove me crazy. In the long run, I’ve found that fighting for her fuels my desire to succeed. Sizing * I am wearing size small in the picture - I am 6'0ft 165lbs *

name: CHAOS IN MIND
description: CHAOS IN MIND Another shirt designed along with the FASHION ASYLUM shirt during the difficult time immediately following the abduction of my daughter Nadia. It expresses my internal thoughts about faith, peace of mind, patience and the one thing that has kept me sane as I continue fighting for Nadia...chasing my dreams. Sizing * I am wearing size small in the picture - I am 6'0ft 165lbs *

name: NADIA LYNN FOUNDATION
NADIA LYNN FOUNDATION II
description: DONATE TO THE NADIA LYNN FOUNDATION Foundation started for my internationally abducted daughter. My goal is to raise as much money as possible to not only help fund my costly international legal battle overseas in Brazil, but to also one day be able to provide financial support for other left behind fathers in a similar situation who cannot afford to begin this lengthy and costly battle for their abducted children. I've began the Give Eight Grand challenge for my Foundation. It's my goal to raise at least eight thousand dollars by November 11, 2011. This is enough money to provide FOUR left behind parents roundtrip tickets to travel and stay in Brazil for their court hearing or visitation with their children. Proceeds from t-shirt purchases will go towards the foundation as well. NADIA NCMEC ABDUCTION POSTER MY STORY THANK YOU -Devon Davenport [Father of Nadia Lynn]
